title: Attractive & Spacious 1BR/1BA, Hardwood, Parking, Laundry. Location!!
posting_body: ['Location : 4096 17th Street', 'PROPERTY DETAILS:', '* Charming and spacious 1 BR/1 BA in well maintained building', '* upper unit w/great views and lots of light throughout and quite green patch view', '* Remodeled Kitchen with custom cabinets, granite countertop and refrigerator', '* Expansive island bar', '* double-pane windows', '* Hardwood floors', '* Walk-in closet space t : bedroom closet, linen closet and additional storage space', '* Coin-operated laundry in building', '* Covered secured remote operated Parking spot', "* Walker's Paradise!", 'Walking score of 98 -- walking distance to Corona Heights Park, restaurants, cafes, shopping', '* Excellent Transit!', 'Transit score of 96 -- walking distance to Castro Street MUNI station, public transportation, Tech shuttles, ride sharing', 'LEASE TERMS:', '* One (1) year lease', '* Monthly rent: $2800.00', '* Security Deposit: $3,000.00', '* Utilities: Tenant(s) pay PG&E / Landlord pays Water and Garbage', '* Pets allowed with $400 pet deposit', '* Non-smoking building']
